title: Missing PPVCORE
message:
Liquide yes.

When All_SYS_PWRGD is present that mean all is ok except cpu core??

title: Missing PPVCORE
message: ALL_SYS then all rails should be running. No Vcore can be anything, the CPU needs to talk to U7400 to enable it. No U7400 is never bad. R7402/03 are suspect. Inspect board for corrosion.
